    <DisplayName>Time Log Premium</DisplayName>
    <Description xml:space="preserve">Full-featured, usage-based time tracking for Azure DevOps. Log time against work items, keep Completed and Remaining in sync, and report across teams. Free 30-day trial, no card required.</Description>
